Sarah E. Allen, Appellant, v. Barnard E. Kilgore, Trustee in Bankruptcy of the Estate of J. J. Mendenhall, Bankrupt, Appellee. An appeal from a Decree of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Pinellas. Howard P. Macfarlane, for Appellant; • Lucas & Withers, for Appellee.

Appeal dismissed on motion of counsel' for appellant.
